creator: Developpeurs Qualios
descriptionHtml:
Documented information management application for Qualios DOC & Qualios MANAGER software.

To be able to take full benefit of this mobile application, it must be linked to your Qualios DOC and/or Qualios Manager EDM software solution for the management of your information system and QMS.

At any time :
- Consult and search documents stored in your EDM
- Keep informed of new documents and document revisions in your EDM through notifications
- Validate and acknowledge your documents from your smartphone
- Manage your own favorite documents
- Upload your documents from EDM to your smartphone and share them!
- Access your forms online
- Customize your start menus
- EDM available in offline mode
- Synchronize your document management actions offline

Direct access to your tasks and to all the documents you need for your business, anywhere, anytime!

creator: Developpeurs Qualios
descriptionHtml:
Documented information management application for Qualios DOC & Qualios MANAGER software.

To be able to take full benefit of this mobile application, it must be linked to your Qualios DOC and/or Qualios Manager EDM software solution for the management of your information system and QMS.

At any time :
- Consult and search documents stored in your EDM
- Keep informed of new documents and document revisions in your EDM through notifications
- Validate and acknowledge your documents from your smartphone
- Manage your own favorite documents
- Upload your documents from EDM to your smartphone and share them!
- Access your forms online
- Customize your start menus
- EDM available in offline mode
- Synchronize your document management actions offline
- Complete your forms in offline
- ModeSynchronize the input of your offline forms


Direct access to your tasks and to all the documents you need for your business, anywhere, anytime!
Customize the menu of your Qualios mobile application and complete your forms offline or online !
